*nco-3.2.0 (27 Apr 2007)

  27 Apr 2007; Sébastien Fabbro <bicatali@gentoo.org> metadata.xml,
  +nco-3.2.0.ebuild:
  Version bump. Added functionality through new use flags: mpi, udunits and
  ncap2. Proper documentation and longdescription added to metadata.xml.
  Closing bug #160843. Thanks to Stefan Nickl <snickl@snickl.freaks.de> for his initial ebuild.

  09 Feb 2007; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> ChangeLog:
  Regenerate digest in Manifest2 format.

  26 Jun 2005; Olivier Fisette <ribosome@gentoo.org> -nco-2.2.0.ebuild,
  -nco-2.7.1.ebuild, nco-2.9.1.ebuild:
  Added to x86. Removed obsolete versions.

  06 May 2005; David Holm <dholm@gentoo.org> nco-2.9.1.ebuild:
  Added to ~ppc.

